    title: "Running total of positive numbers",
    bullets: ["Keep asking for numbers and add them to Total while Number > 0. Stop when non-positive entered."],
    hint: "Initialise Total=0; INPUT Number; WHILE Number > 0 DO Total = Total + Number; INPUT Number; ENDWHILE.",
    example: "Inputs 5,3,-1 â†’ The total is 8",
    lines: [
